text: Ozren Grabarić (born 17 July 1980) is a Croatian actor, member of the Gavella Theatre in Zagreb,HINKEMANN Mračna i uznemirujuća predstava prema tekstu genijalnog dramatičara often featured in TV series and in film.HAVC - SVE NAJBOLJE! He is a professor at the Academy of Dramatic Art in Zagreb. He voiced Crane in the Croatian dub of the Kung Fu Panda films. ==References== Category:1980 births Category:Living people Category:Actors from Zagreb
